[SPEAKER_00] je 2022. godine

348
00:17:08,279 --> 00:17:09,339
[SPEAKER_00] papa je proglasio

349
00:17:09,339 --> 00:17:10,539
[SPEAKER_00] Irenea Lijonskog

350
00:17:10,539 --> 00:17:11,680
[SPEAKER_00] koja je živio u drugom stoljeću

351
00:17:11,680 --> 00:17:12,579
[SPEAKER_00] crkvenim naučiteljem,

352
00:17:12,579 --> 00:17:13,759
[SPEAKER_00] što je dobra vijest jer ima nade

353
00:17:13,759 --> 00:17:14,700
[SPEAKER_00] za sve nas još ovdje.

354
00:17:14,700 --> 00:17:17,039
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro,

355
00:17:17,039 --> 00:17:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] učiteljstvo.

356
00:17:19,000 --> 00:17:20,319
[SPEAKER_00] Sad se vraćam na ovo učiteljstvo,

357
00:17:20,319 --> 00:17:21,559
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno na taj zbor biskupa.

358
00:17:21,559 --> 00:17:24,839
[SPEAKER_00] Katekizam 85 kaže ovako.

359
00:17:24,839 --> 00:17:27,720
[SPEAKER_00] Zadača autentičnog tumačenja,

360
00:17:27,720 --> 00:17:29,880
[SPEAKER_00] pisane ili predane Božje riječi,

361
00:17:29,880 --> 00:17:32,640
[SPEAKER_00] povjerena je samo živom crkvenom učiteljstvu,

362
00:17:32,640 --> 00:17:35,380
[SPEAKER_00] koje tu vlast obnaša u ime Isusa Krista,

363
00:17:35,779 --> 00:17:37,480
[SPEAKER_00] to jest biskupima u zajedništu

364
00:17:37,480 --> 00:17:39,279
[SPEAKER_00] s Petrovim naslednikom papom.

365
00:17:39,279 --> 00:17:41,460
[SPEAKER_00] To učiteljstvo dakako

366
00:17:41,460 --> 00:17:43,160
[SPEAKER_00] nije iznad riječi Božje,

367
00:17:43,160 --> 00:17:45,019
[SPEAKER_00] nego joj služi naučavajući

368
00:17:45,019 --> 00:17:46,599
[SPEAKER_00] samo ono što je predano.

369
00:17:46,599 --> 00:17:48,019
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

370
00:17:48,019 --> 00:17:49,559
[SPEAKER_00] pojednostavajući taj odnos,

371
00:17:49,559 --> 00:17:50,680
[SPEAKER_00] predaja,

372
00:17:50,680 --> 00:17:52,500
[SPEAKER_00] rasvjetljava sveto pismo,

373
00:17:52,500 --> 00:17:53,400
[SPEAKER_00] tumači ga

374
00:17:53,400 --> 00:17:55,380
[SPEAKER_00] i iznose neke vjerske istine

375
00:17:55,380 --> 00:17:57,660
[SPEAKER_00] koje ili nisu jasne u svetom pismu

376
00:17:57,660 --> 00:17:59,180
[SPEAKER_00] ili se ne nalaze u svetom pismu.

377
00:18:00,119 --> 00:18:01,640
[SPEAKER_00] A učiteljstvo ima zadaču

378
00:18:01,640 --> 00:18:02,859
[SPEAKER_00] autentično tumačiti

379
00:18:02,859 --> 00:18:04,099
[SPEAKER_00] i svetu predaju

380
00:18:04,099 --> 00:18:05,160
[SPEAKER_00] i sveto pismo.

381
00:18:05,160 --> 00:18:08,599
[SPEAKER_00] I tu bih htio istaknuti

382
00:18:08,599 --> 00:18:09,299
[SPEAKER_00] koliko je zapravo

383
00:18:09,299 --> 00:18:10,880
[SPEAKER_00] uloga predaje

384
00:18:10,880 --> 00:18:12,099
[SPEAKER_00] ključna u tom odnosu.

385
00:18:12,099 --> 00:18:14,039
[SPEAKER_00] Jer da nema predaje,

386
00:18:14,039 --> 00:18:15,660
[SPEAKER_00] učiteljstvo bi u teoriji moglo,

387
00:18:15,660 --> 00:18:18,039
[SPEAKER_00] kad bi imali neke liberalne biskupe,

388
00:18:18,039 --> 00:18:19,980
[SPEAKER_00] naći opravdanje

389
00:18:19,980 --> 00:18:21,880
[SPEAKER_00] u sljedećem redku.

390
00:18:21,880 --> 00:18:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Aj, prvo ću ga pročitati,

391
00:18:23,000 --> 00:18:23,819
[SPEAKER_00] pa ćete razumijeti.

392
00:18:23,819 --> 00:18:27,259
[SPEAKER_00] Druva knjiga o Sameliju 1.26.

393
00:18:27,900 --> 00:18:29,579
[SPEAKER_00] Davidu je njegov prijatelj Jonatan

394
00:18:29,579 --> 00:18:30,180
[SPEAKER_00] upravo umro.

395
00:18:30,180 --> 00:18:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] I kaže ovako.

396
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:32,900
[SPEAKER_00] Žao mi je tebe, brate Jonatane,

397
00:18:32,900 --> 00:18:34,720
[SPEAKER_00] kako li mi, drag, bijaše ti veoma.

398
00:18:34,720 --> 00:18:36,700
[SPEAKER_00] Ljubav tvoja biješe meni

399
00:18:36,700 --> 00:18:38,180
[SPEAKER_00] još od ženske čudesnija.

400
00:18:38,180 --> 00:18:40,460
[SPEAKER_00] I onda kada bi imali

401
00:18:40,460 --> 00:18:41,619
[SPEAKER_00] neke liberalne biskupe,

402
00:18:41,619 --> 00:18:42,740
[SPEAKER_00] oni bi to mogli tumačiti

403
00:18:42,740 --> 00:18:44,019
[SPEAKER_00] kao opravdanje

404
00:18:44,019 --> 00:18:45,799
[SPEAKER_00] za homoseksualnu ljubav u Bibliji.

405
00:18:45,799 --> 00:18:47,259
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, tradicija je ta

406
00:18:47,259 --> 00:18:48,680
[SPEAKER_00] koja je čuvarica pologa

407
00:18:48,680 --> 00:18:50,099
[SPEAKER_00] i upravo kada pogleda,

408
00:18:50,099 --> 00:18:51,940
[SPEAKER_00] upravo tradicija nudi mogućnost

409
00:18:51,940 --> 00:18:54,019
[SPEAKER_00] da mi vidimo kako je crkva tumačila

410
00:18:54,019 --> 00:18:56,960
[SPEAKER_00] od najranjih vrmena pa do danas te retke

411
00:18:56,960 --> 00:18:58,980
[SPEAKER_00] i tu zapravo štiti

412
00:18:58,980 --> 00:19:02,599
[SPEAKER_00] brani od mogućnosti huljenja na taj način.

413
00:19:02,599 --> 00:19:06,759
[SPEAKER_00] I ovo bi povezu sa današnjom situacijom,

414
00:19:06,759 --> 00:19:08,420
[SPEAKER_00] primjer Katoličke crkve u Njemačkoj

415
00:19:08,420 --> 00:19:10,539
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je raskol praktički pred vratima,

416
00:19:10,539 --> 00:19:12,539
[SPEAKER_00] samo što se nije dogodio.

417
00:19:13,019 --> 00:19:15,619
[SPEAKER_00] I upravo je ovo pitanje,

418
00:19:15,619 --> 00:19:17,440
[SPEAKER_00] pitanje homoseksualizma,

419
00:19:17,440 --> 00:19:19,359
[SPEAKER_00] jedno od gorućih pitanja,

420
00:19:19,359 --> 00:19:19,960
[SPEAKER_00] prijelomnih.

421
00:19:19,960 --> 00:19:23,220
[SPEAKER_00] Homoseksualizam je jasno osuđen

422
00:19:23,220 --> 00:19:24,819
[SPEAKER_00] i u Starom zavetu i u Novom zavetu,

423
00:19:24,819 --> 00:19:28,279
[SPEAKER_00] ali današnji hiperseksualiziran društvo

424
00:19:28,279 --> 00:19:31,019
[SPEAKER_00] ne može shvatiti da može postojiti

425
00:19:31,019 --> 00:19:33,039
[SPEAKER_00] takva bliskost između Davida i Jonatana

426
00:19:33,039 --> 00:19:34,779
[SPEAKER_00] bez da bude seksualna.

427
00:19:34,779 --> 00:19:38,140
[SPEAKER_00] Na sličan način obtužuju mnoge

428
00:19:38,140 --> 00:19:40,140
[SPEAKER_00] crkvene svece,

429
00:19:40,140 --> 00:19:42,019
[SPEAKER_00] kad god imate svece, sveticu,

430
00:19:42,019 --> 00:19:43,200
[SPEAKER_00] da su bili blisko i prijatelji,

431
00:19:43,200 --> 00:19:45,579
[SPEAKER_00] onda uvijek tu dovode nekakve aluzije

432
00:19:45,579 --> 00:19:47,460
[SPEAKER_00] u nečednost njihovog odnosa.

433
00:19:47,460 --> 00:19:49,759
[SPEAKER_00] Jer, kao što sam rekao,

434
00:19:49,759 --> 00:19:52,079
[SPEAKER_00] društvo naše svjetsko,

435
00:19:52,079 --> 00:19:54,440
[SPEAKER_00] sekularno, hiperseksualizirano društvo

436
00:19:54,440 --> 00:19:55,480
[SPEAKER_00] to ne može pojmiti.

437
00:19:55,480 --> 00:19:58,839
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što je bitno je

438
00:19:58,839 --> 00:20:00,960
[SPEAKER_00] da ti kad napustiš zdrav nauk,

439
00:20:00,960 --> 00:20:03,299
[SPEAKER_00] nauk sve te predaje,

440
00:20:03,299 --> 00:20:05,819
[SPEAKER_00] i kad se odvojiš na taj način od Božje istine,

441
00:20:05,819 --> 00:20:06,799
[SPEAKER_00] Bog to ne trpi.

442
00:20:06,799 --> 00:20:08,599
[SPEAKER_00] I Bog, ne zato što je on tiranin,

443
00:20:08,660 --> 00:20:10,160
[SPEAKER_00] nego zato što želi naše spasanje

444
00:20:10,160 --> 00:20:12,319
[SPEAKER_00] i ne želi da ustremo na putu koji vodi u pakao,

445
00:20:12,319 --> 00:20:13,799
[SPEAKER_00] će razoriti te zajednice.

446
00:20:13,799 --> 00:20:15,200
[SPEAKER_00] I on će razoriti te crkve.

447
00:20:15,200 --> 00:20:18,859
[SPEAKER_00] I upravo vidimo da se nešto slično dešava

448
00:20:18,859 --> 00:20:20,220
[SPEAKER_00] sa katoličkom crkom u Njemačkoj

449
00:20:20,220 --> 00:20:21,539
[SPEAKER_00] i nekim drugim crkvama.

450
00:20:21,539 --> 00:20:24,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što me posebno smeta je

451
00:20:24,880 --> 00:20:27,640
[SPEAKER_00] da upravo po toj liberalno-njemačkoj teologiji,

452
00:20:27,640 --> 00:20:30,940
[SPEAKER_00] koja je ispraznila Europske crkve,

453
00:20:31,880 --> 00:20:34,779
[SPEAKER_00] naši pastiri i naši teolozi stasaju

454
00:20:34,779 --> 00:20:35,619
[SPEAKER_00] i obrazuju se.

455
00:20:35,619 --> 00:20:38,940
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, danas na fakultetima teologije

456
00:20:38,940 --> 00:20:42,420
[SPEAKER_00] jedva da imate koji kolege iz patristike,

457
00:20:42,420 --> 00:20:45,079
[SPEAKER_00] patrologije, dakle kolege koji obrađaju crkvene oce,

458
00:20:45,079 --> 00:20:48,539
[SPEAKER_00] maknuli su angelologiju, demonologiju,

459
00:20:48,539 --> 00:20:50,759
[SPEAKER_00] znači ti se školuješ za Kristovog ratnika,

460
00:20:50,759 --> 00:20:51,980
[SPEAKER_00] ne znaš protiv kog se boriš,

461
00:20:51,980 --> 00:20:53,599
[SPEAKER_00] ne znaš ko su ti najbolji saveznici.

462
00:20:55,640 --> 00:20:57,299
[SPEAKER_00] Naučitelje, pitanje je da li su opće čitali,

463
00:20:57,299 --> 00:20:58,680
[SPEAKER_00] pitanje je da li ih znaju nabrojati.

464
00:20:58,680 --> 00:21:01,819
[SPEAKER_00] U redu.

465
00:21:01,819 --> 00:21:05,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde, ovo je bio malo oštri dio.

466
00:21:05,519 --> 00:21:11,140
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto je pravo vjerije toliko bitno?

467
00:21:11,140 --> 00:21:12,700
[SPEAKER_00] Toma Akvinski kaže,

468
00:21:12,700 --> 00:21:14,700
[SPEAKER_00] i katekizam pijadesetog to isto kaže,

469
00:21:14,700 --> 00:21:17,059
[SPEAKER_00] da samo jedna hereza, pazi ovo,

470
00:21:17,059 --> 00:21:19,880
[SPEAKER_00] samo jedna hereza može iskvariti

471
00:21:19,880 --> 00:21:23,799
[SPEAKER_00] i kvari cijelokupnu bogoslovnu vrlinu vjere.

472
00:21:24,619 --> 00:21:26,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ovdje ne govorimo o karizmi vjere,

473
00:21:26,039 --> 00:21:28,140
[SPEAKER_00] ovdje govorimo o vrlini vjere.

474
00:21:28,140 --> 00:21:31,059
[SPEAKER_00] A vrlina vjere se definira kao davanje

475
00:21:31,059 --> 00:21:34,779
[SPEAKER_00] vlastitog pristanka vjerskim istinama

476
00:21:34,779 --> 00:21:35,839
[SPEAKER_00] kojima nas crkva uči.

477
00:21:35,839 --> 00:21:38,599
[SPEAKER_00] I sad to možda zvuči onako,

478
00:21:38,599 --> 00:21:40,440
[SPEAKER_00] ok, pa jel baš cijelu vrlinu vjere

479
00:21:40,440 --> 00:21:41,980
[SPEAKER_00] može kvariti kad nije to malo preoštro?

480
00:21:41,980 --> 00:21:43,180
[SPEAKER_00] Ali daću jedan primjer,

481
00:21:43,180 --> 00:21:45,279
[SPEAKER_00] biću malo simplificiraću ga,

482
00:21:45,279 --> 00:21:46,299
[SPEAKER_00] biću plastičan.

483
00:21:46,299 --> 00:21:47,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ali upravo zbog toga što su vjerske istine

484
00:21:47,980 --> 00:21:49,940
[SPEAKER_00] koherentne i čine jedan smislen niz,

485
00:21:49,940 --> 00:21:52,160
[SPEAKER_00] ti dovodeći u sumnju jednu,

486
00:21:52,839 --> 00:21:54,759
[SPEAKER_00] dovodeći u sumnju i druge.

487
00:21:54,759 --> 00:21:55,539
[SPEAKER_00] Na primjer,

488
00:21:55,539 --> 00:21:58,480
[SPEAKER_00] ja ako volim Mariju,

489
00:21:58,480 --> 00:21:59,619
[SPEAKER_00] pa ću mu uzeti marijanski primjer.

490
00:21:59,619 --> 00:22:02,380
[SPEAKER_00] Recimo da netko ne bi vjerovao

491
00:22:02,380 --> 00:22:05,200
[SPEAKER_00] i kad bi tvrdio da...

492
00:22:05,200 --> 00:22:06,259
[SPEAKER_00] Sad sam skužio.

493
00:22:06,259 --> 00:22:10,279
[SPEAKER_00] Sad sam skužio.

494
00:22:20,839 --> 00:22:26,920
[SPEAKER_00] Kad bi netko tvrdio da djevica Marija

495
00:22:26,920 --> 00:22:28,019
[SPEAKER_00] nije bezgrašna začeta,

496
00:22:28,019 --> 00:22:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] onda ona ne bi bila sačuvana

497
00:22:31,000 --> 00:22:32,339
[SPEAKER_00] od ljage istočnog grijeha.

498
00:22:32,339 --> 00:22:34,079
[SPEAKER_00] A onda se postavlja pitanje,

499
00:22:34,079 --> 00:22:36,519
[SPEAKER_00] bili krist utilovljen i mogao proći

500
00:22:36,519 --> 00:22:38,180
[SPEAKER_00] kroz ono što bi u tom slučaju

501
00:22:38,180 --> 00:22:40,160
[SPEAKER_00] bio okaljan i medi i ne okaljati se.

502
00:22:40,160 --> 00:22:41,819
[SPEAKER_00] A kad bi on bio okaljan,

503
00:22:41,819 --> 00:22:44,220
[SPEAKER_00] to bi joj činilo žrtvu na križu

504
00:22:44,220 --> 00:22:46,039
[SPEAKER_00] manje vrijednom,

505
00:22:47,160 --> 00:22:48,819
[SPEAKER_00] nesavršenom i manje zaslužnom.

506
00:22:48,819 --> 00:22:50,660
[SPEAKER_00] Znači vi ste u tri koraka

507
00:22:50,660 --> 00:22:52,259
[SPEAKER_00] došli do jedne vrlo, vrlo, vrlo

508
00:22:52,259 --> 00:22:53,759
[SPEAKER_00] bogohulne konstatacije.

509
00:22:53,759 --> 00:22:56,240
[SPEAKER_00] Njekajući nešto što se

510
00:22:56,240 --> 00:22:58,519
[SPEAKER_00] nekim protestantskim denominacijama,

511
00:22:58,519 --> 00:22:59,619
[SPEAKER_00] općenim do protestantima,

512
00:22:59,619 --> 00:23:01,720
[SPEAKER_00] čini kao zabloda

513
00:23:01,720 --> 00:23:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] u koju katolička crkva vjeruje.

514
00:23:03,000 --> 00:23:05,420
[SPEAKER_00] Protestanti imaju doktrinu

515
00:23:05,420 --> 00:23:06,700
[SPEAKER_00] znanu kao sola skriptura,

516
00:23:06,700 --> 00:23:08,160
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno samo sve to pismo.

517
00:23:08,440 --> 00:23:09,599
[SPEAKER_00] I po tim oni vjeruju

518
00:23:09,599 --> 00:23:11,579
[SPEAKER_00] i podrazumijevaju da je Biblija

519
00:23:11,579 --> 00:23:13,480
[SPEAKER_00] jedini autoritativni izvor

520
00:23:13,480 --> 00:23:14,539
[SPEAKER_00] spoznaje za vjernika.

521
00:23:14,539 --> 00:23:17,559
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, da u njoj leži sva istina

522
00:23:17,559 --> 00:23:20,519
[SPEAKER_00] i da je ona jedino duhovnom vrelo

523
00:23:20,519 --> 00:23:22,019
[SPEAKER_00] iz kojeg proizlazi sve bitno

524
00:23:22,019 --> 00:23:23,359
[SPEAKER_00] za vjeru i praksu kršćanina.

525
00:23:23,359 --> 00:23:26,200
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, tu ima nekoliko problema.

526
00:23:26,200 --> 00:23:28,039
[SPEAKER_00] Nigde u Bibliji se ne može naći

527
00:23:28,039 --> 00:23:29,200
[SPEAKER_00] podloga za takvo mišljenje.

528
00:23:29,660 --> 00:23:30,960
[SPEAKER_00] Drugo, bilo bi kontraditorno

529
00:23:30,960 --> 00:23:33,400
[SPEAKER_00] samom svetom pismu vjerovati u to,

530
00:23:33,400 --> 00:23:35,240
[SPEAKER_00] jer te upravo samo sveto pismo,

531
00:23:35,240 --> 00:23:36,700
[SPEAKER_00] kao što ću kasnije pokazati,

532
00:23:36,700 --> 00:23:40,500
[SPEAKER_00] upućuje na neke van svetopisamske tekstove i stvari.

533
00:23:40,500 --> 00:23:46,960
[SPEAKER_00] Uz to, bitno je uvidjeti da

534
00:23:46,960 --> 00:23:48,839
[SPEAKER_00] sveto pismo nije palo s neba.

535
00:23:48,839 --> 00:23:52,019
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, zovemo ga svetim pismom.

536
00:23:52,019 --> 00:23:54,039
[SPEAKER_00] Netkom je morao dati atribut svetog.

537
00:23:54,039 --> 00:23:56,440
[SPEAKER_00] A upravo je crkva ta koja ga prepozna

538
00:23:56,440 --> 00:23:58,039
[SPEAKER_00] i odobrava kao svetog.

539
00:23:58,359 --> 00:24:00,099
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, svaka čast nekom pastoru

540
00:24:00,099 --> 00:24:01,819
[SPEAKER_00] koji se nazvao pastorom,

541
00:24:01,819 --> 00:24:03,759
[SPEAKER_00] obukao dijelo i počeo propovjedati

542
00:24:03,759 --> 00:24:06,240
[SPEAKER_00] i svjedočiti da je Biblija autentična Bože riječ.

543
00:24:06,240 --> 00:24:07,779
[SPEAKER_00] To sve stoji i je,

544
00:24:07,779 --> 00:24:10,500
[SPEAKER_00] ali on nema autoritet da on kaže

545
00:24:10,500 --> 00:24:11,980
